      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. so if you're saying the intervention was a miscalculation because of the power vacuum, does that mean that most liberal interventionism is just fundamentally flawed? like, can you ever actually justify these kinds of \"humanitarian\" missions if they always end up creating these massive security holes?",
